trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for the collection that is specified by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items*> property of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir et redigeringsprogram for komponenten for samlingen som er angitt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items*>for den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items*>

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem> elements of the collection that is specified by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A> property within the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MenuItemCollectionEditor gir et brukergrensesnitt for redigering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem>elementer i samlingen som er angitt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A>egenskapen i den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItem>

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemCollectionEditor is invoked by selecting the ellipsis (**…**) button on the **Items** property in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer, or by choosing **Edit Menu Items** from the **Common Tasks** context menu on the control.
trans-unit.target: MenuItemCollectionEditor aktiveres ved å velge ellipsen (**... **)-knappen på den **elementer** egenskap i den **Egenskaper** rutenett for den visuelle utformeren, eller ved å velge **Rediger menyelementer** fra den **vanlige oppgaver** hurtigmenyen kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A> method edits the values of the menu item collection of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A>metoden redigerer verdiene i menyen elementsamlingen for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A> method gets the editing style that is associated with this editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A>metoden henter redigering stilen som er knyttet til dette redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor> class when you select the ellipsis (**…**) button on the **Items** property in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer when designing the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control, or choose **Edit Menu Items** from the **Common Tasks** context menu on the control.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor>Når du velger ellipsen (**... **)-knappen på den **elementer** egenskap i den **Egenskaper** rutenett med den visuelle utformeren når du utformer den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollere, eller velg **Rediger menyelementer** fra den **vanlige oppgaver** hurtigmenyen kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: Edits the value of the menu item collection of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Redigerer verdien for menyen elementsamlingen for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The EditValue method extracts the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> object that is associated with that control from the `context` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Metoden EditValue trekker ut den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>objektet som er forbundet med denne kontrollen fra den `context` parameteren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: Then the EditValue calls back on the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> to display an editing dialog box that is used to edit the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection> object of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: EditValue kaller deretter tilbake på den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>til å vise en redigering dialogboks som brukes til å redigere den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection>objekt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The `provider` parameter is not used.
trans-unit.target: Den `provider` parameteren er ikke brukt.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that is used to acquire context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som brukes til å hente informasjon om sikkerhetskontekst.

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the <xref:System.IServiceProvider> through which editing services can be obtained.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.IServiceProvider>som redigering services kan hentes.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The object to edit the value for.
trans-unit.target: Objektet til å redigere verdien for.

trans-unit.source: The new value; otherwise, if the value of the object has not changed, value unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Den nye value ; Ellers hvis verdien for objektet ikke er endret, value uendret.

trans-unit.source: Gets the editing style that is associated with this editor.
trans-unit.target: Henter redigering stilen som er knyttet til dette redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: The GetEditStyle method always returns the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle> value, which indicates that the user interface for the editor is a modal dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetEditStyle returnerer alltid den <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>-verdi som angir at brukergrensesnittet for redigeringsprogrammet er en modal dialogboks.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>

trans-unit.source: The `context` parameter is not used.
trans-unit.target: Den `context` parameteren er ikke brukt.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that indicates the context of the object being edited.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som angir konteksten for objektet som redigeres.

trans-unit.source: Always returns <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer alltid <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"> </xref>.
